{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, basically we have public leaders,"},{"time":3000,"text":"public officials who are out of control;"},{"time":6000,"text":"they are writing bills that are unintelligible,"},{"time":8000,"text":"and out of these bills are going to come"},{"time":10000,"text":"maybe 40,000 pages of regulations, total complexity,"},{"time":15000,"text":"which has a dramatically negative impact on our life."},{"time":18000,"text":"If you're a veteran coming back from Iraq or Vietnam"},{"time":22000,"text":"you face a blizzard of paperwork to get your benefits;"},{"time":26000,"text":"if you're trying to get a small business loan,"},{"time":28000,"text":"you face a blizzard of paperwork."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"What are we going to do about it? I define simplicity"},{"time":32000,"text":"as a means to achieving clarity,"},{"time":35000,"text":"transparency and empathy,"},{"time":37000,"text":"building humanity into communications."},{"time":40000,"text":"I've been simplifying things for 30 years."},{"time":43000,"text":"I come out of the advertising and design business."},{"time":46000,"text":"My focus is understanding you people,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and how you interact with the government"},{"time":52000,"text":"to get your benefits,"},{"time":54000,"text":"how you interact with corporations to decide whom you're going to do business with,"},{"time":57000,"text":"and how you view brands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"So, very quickly, when President Obama said,"},{"time":64000,"text":"\"I don't see why we can't"},{"time":66000,"text":"have a one-page, plain English consumer credit agreement.\""},{"time":70000,"text":"So, I locked myself in a room,"},{"time":72000,"text":"figured out the content,"},{"time":75000,"text":"organized the document, and wrote it in plain English."},{"time":78000,"text":"I've had this checked by the two top"},{"time":80000,"text":"consumer credit lawyers in the country."},{"time":82000,"text":"This is a real thing."},{"time":84000,"text":"Now, I went one step further and said,"},{"time":87000,"text":"\"Why do we have to stick with the stodgy lawyers"},{"time":89000,"text":"and just have a paper document? Let's go online.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"And many people"},{"time":95000,"text":"might need help in computation."},{"time":97000,"text":"Working with the Harvard Business School,"},{"time":99000,"text":"you'll see this example when you talk about minimum payment:"},{"time":103000,"text":"If you spent 62 dollars for a meal,"},{"time":106000,"text":"the longer you take to pay out that loan,"},{"time":109000,"text":"you see, over a period of time using the minimum payment"},{"time":111000,"text":"it's 99 dollars and 17 cents."},{"time":114000,"text":"How about that? Do you think your bank is going to show that to people?"},{"time":117000,"text":"But it's going to work. It's more effective"},{"time":119000,"text":"than just computational aids."},{"time":121000,"text":"And what about terms like"},{"time":123000,"text":"\"over the limit\"?"},{"time":126000,"text":"Perhaps a stealth thing."},{"time":128000,"text":"Define it in context. Tell people what it means."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"When you put it in plain English,"},{"time":132000,"text":"you almost force the institution"},{"time":134000,"text":"to give the people a way, a default out of that,"},{"time":136000,"text":"and not put themselves at risk."},{"time":138000,"text":"Plain English is about"},{"time":141000,"text":"changing the content."},{"time":143000,"text":"And one of the things I'm most proud of"},{"time":145000,"text":"is this agreement for IBM."},{"time":147000,"text":"It's a grid, it's a calendar."},{"time":149000,"text":"At such and such a date, IBM has responsibilities,"},{"time":151000,"text":"you have responsibilities."},{"time":153000,"text":"Received very favorably by business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"And there is some good news to report today."},{"time":159000,"text":"Each year, one in 10 taxpayers"},{"time":161000,"text":"receives a notice from the IRS."},{"time":163000,"text":"There are 200 million letters that go out."},{"time":166000,"text":"Running through this typical letter that they had,"},{"time":169000,"text":"I ran it through my simplicity lab,"},{"time":171000,"text":"it's pretty unintelligible."},{"time":173000,"text":"All the parts of the document in red are not intelligible."},{"time":177000,"text":"We looked at doing over 1,000 letters that cover"},{"time":179000,"text":"70 percent of their transactions in plain English."},{"time":182000,"text":"They have been tested in the laboratory."},{"time":184000,"text":"When I run it through my lab,"},{"time":186000,"text":"this heat-mapping shows everything"},{"time":188000,"text":"is intelligible."},{"time":190000,"text":"And the IRS has introduced the program."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"There are a couple of things going on right now"},{"time":200000,"text":"that I want to bring to your attention."},{"time":202000,"text":"There is a lot of discussion now"},{"time":204000,"text":"about a consumer financial protection agency,"},{"time":206000,"text":"how to mandate simplicity."},{"time":208000,"text":"We see all this complexity."},{"time":210000,"text":"It's incumbent upon us,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and this organization, I believe,"},{"time":214000,"text":"to make clarity, transparency"},{"time":217000,"text":"and empathy a national priority."},{"time":220000,"text":"There is no way that we should allow government"},{"time":222000,"text":"to communicate the way they communicate."},{"time":224000,"text":"There is no way we should do business"},{"time":226000,"text":"with companies that have agreements"},{"time":229000,"text":"with stealth provisions and that are unintelligible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"So, how are we going to change the world?"},{"time":233000,"text":"Make clarity, transparency and simplicity a national priority."},{"time":238000,"text":"I thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}